Choices-cs.utf-8: ano, ne, zeptat se
Choices-da.utf-8: ja, nej, spørg
Choices-de.utf-8: Ja, Nein, Fragen
Choices-es.utf-8: sí, no, preguntar
Choices-eu.utf-8: bai, ez, galdetu
Choices-fi.utf-8: kyllä, ei, kysy
